data.description:
Introducing a meticulously updated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom ranch-style home at 2940 Teakwood Manor Dr. Nestled in a serene neighborhood, this residence offers the perfect blend of comfort and style.

Inside, discover a spacious living area and an open-concept design that effortlessly connects the living room, dining area, and spacious kitchen. Ideal for both daily living and entertaining, this space is the true heart of the home.

The kitchen boasts sleek countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample cabinet space, making meals a joy. 

The lower level reveals a finished basement, offering extra sleep space, a recreational area, or a potential home gym!

Located in a friendly community, this home is within easy reach of parks, schools, and shopping, promising a convenient lifestyle. With its updates, spacious layout, and charming outdoor spaces, 2940 Teakwood Manor Dr. is ready to welcome you home. Don't miss your chance to make it your own. Schedule a showing today!
